-- Ukraine to Pump 5 Billion Cubic Meters Shale Gas, Izvestia Says
-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 2011-12-23T08:54:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-23/ukraine-to-pump-5-billion-cubic-meters-shale-gas-izvestia-says.html
Ukraine wants to extract 4 billion
to 5 billion cubic meters of shale gas a year by 2020,
 Ekonomicheskie Izvestia  newspaper reported, citing NAK Naftogaz
Ukrainy Deputy Chief Executive Officer Vadym Chuprun.  Chuprun also said  Exxon Mobil Corp. (XOM)  “has expressed
interest” in renting out Ukraine’s storage facilities to export
gas to  Europe , according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
 akrasnolutska@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
 bpenz@bloomberg.net  